Install apache from source on rockhounding.net linode system.


1.  Build the apache portable runtime project (APR) 
    Debian packages (*.deb).

i. Get apr-util:
$ wget http://ftp.wayne.edu/apache//apr/apr-1.6.3.tar.gz

ii. Compile apache portable runtime:
$ tar zxvpf apr-1.6.3.tar.gz
$ cd apr-1.6.3/
$ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
$ make



